<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-12-1098 </DOCNO><TEXT>The terms of radioactivity and the issues of radioactivity transport throughthe atmosphere, its effect on living organisms and its incorporationinto the human body are discussed from a nuclear opponent's point ofview. The survey-type compilation of issues alone suffices to feel theneed for immediate cancellation of nuclear energy.</TEXT></DOC>